 England":"영국 잉글랜드 노르스벌랜드 카람","Morayshire, Scotland":"영국 스코틀랜드 모라이","Argyll, Scotland":"스컷랜드 아그이","Conteville, Calvados, Normandy, France":"프랑스 노먼디 캘바도스 콘테빌","lifeSummary":"Robert De Comyn Earl Of Northumberland(은)는 대략 1020년 프랑스 노먼디 캘바도스 콘테빌에서 John De Tynedale, De Comyn의 아들로 태어났다. 그는 Maud Cumton of Morayshire(와)과 적어도 한 명의 아들을 두었다. 그는 1069년 1월 28일 영국 잉글랜드 노르스벌랜드 카람에서 50세의 나이로 사망했다."},"lv":{"about 1020–28 January 1069":"ap 1020. gadu–1069. gada 28. janvāris","1020–1069":"1020–1069","1026–1053":"1026–1053.gads","1026–Female":"1026–mirusi","1060–1136":"1060–1136","1053–1135":"1053.gads–1135","0991–1021":"0991–1021","about 1060":"ap 1060. gadu","1021":"1021","1053":"1053. gads","1020":"1020","1068–28 January 1069":"no 1068. gada līdz 1069. gada 28. janvārim","1060":"1060","28 January 1069":"1069. gada 28. janvāris","circa 1021":"ap 1021. gadu","1136":"1136","1026":"1026","1135":"1135","1069":"1069","0991":"0991","about 1020":"ap 1020. gadu","about 1053":"ap 1053. gadu","Altyre, Morayshire, Scotland":"Moray, Skotija, Lielbritānija","Durham, Northumberland, England":"Carham, Northumberland, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Morayshire, Scotland":"Moray, Skotija, Lielbritānija","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland","Conteville, Calvados, Normandy, France":"Conteville, Calvados, Normandie, Francija"},"mg":{"about 1020–28 January 1069":"tany ho any amin'ny 1020–28 janoary 1069","1020–1069":"1020–1069","1026–1053":"1026–1053","1026–Female":"1026–Maty","1060–1136":"1060–1136","1053–1135":"1053–1135","0991–1021":"0991–1021","about 1060":"tany ho any amin'ny 1060","1021":"1021","1053":"1053","1020":"1020","1068–28 January 1069":"1068 hatramin'ny 28 janoary 1069","1060":"1060","28 January 1069":"28 janoary 1069","circa 1021":"tany ho any amin'ny 1021","1136":"1136","1026":"1026","1135":"1135","1069":"1069","0991":"0991","about 1020":"tany ho any amin'ny 1020","about 1053":"tany ho any amin'ny 1053","Altyre, Morayshire, Scotland":"Moray, Écosse, United Kingdom","Durham, Northumberland, Engl